> in the mud after death.</li><li style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>• Mud dries and hardens.</li><li style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>• <span class='question-badge'>34</span> <input type='text' id='ans-34' style='width: 180px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #ced6e0; border-radius: 6px; outline: none;'> replace the bones leaving a stone shape.</li></ul><h3 style='color: #2f3542; margin-top: 25px; border-left: 4px solid #e84393; padding-left: 10px;'>Purchasing fossils:</h3><ul style='list-style-type: none; padding-left: 5px;'><li style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>• Site: Shop outside the park or from the park's <span class='question-badge'>35</span> <input type='text' id='ans-35' style='width: 180px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #ced6e0; border-radius: 6px; outline: none;'></li><li style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>• Prices: generally <span class='question-badge'>36</span> <input type='text' id='ans-36' style='width: 180px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #ced6e0; border-radius: 6px; outline: none;'></li></ul></div><div style='background-color: #f1f2f6; border-left: 5px solid #e84393; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;'><strong style='display: block; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 5px;'>Questions 37-40</strong><span style='font-size: 0.9rem; color: #57606f;'>Complete the table below. Write <strong>NO MORE THAN TWO WORDS</strong> for each answer.</span></div><div style='background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e4e7eb; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.8;'><table style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px;'><thead><tr style='border-bottom: 2px solid #e4e7eb; background: #f8f9fa;'><th style='text-align: left; padding: 12px 15px; font-weight: bold; color: #2f3542;'>Tools</th><th style='text-align: left; padding: 12px 15px; font-weight: bold; color: #2f3542;'>Function or purpose</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;'><td style='padding: 12px 15px;'>A tape measure</td><td style='padding: 12px 15px